37:36.379 --> 37:37.347
What about her ?

37:37.687 --> 37:38.237
Squeak.

37:39.200 --> 37:40.055
Offa Lanvale.

37:41.710 --> 37:44.232
Yeah, she used to boost
for Turtle Wells', old mob.

37:44.748 --> 37:46.238
She lost a little bit of weight too.

37:46.249 --> 37:48.208
I mean, lookin' a lot
better than I remember

37:48.395 --> 37:50.073
and I remember a lot
about that girl.

37:51.036 --> 37:53.850
Damn, Bubs, is there anybody
westside you don't know ?

37:54.648 --> 37:56.056
Jus' citizens an' shit.

37:59.246 --> 38:00.675
My C.I. knows the girl.

38:00.990 --> 38:01.812
He can work her ?

38:01.999 --> 38:02.973
If it's smooth, yeah.

38:03.771 --> 38:04.311
Check this.

38:09.892 --> 38:11.014
That's Western District ?

38:11.652 --> 38:13.060
Stringer's calling the Western ?

38:13.271 --> 38:14.667
Maybe he's surrendering.

38:15.453 --> 38:18.270
After all the work we've done,
I'd never forgive the sonofabitch.

38:22.759 --> 38:24.330
Go down. Go down and out.

38:29.667 --> 38:30.313
Sweet !

38:30.583 --> 38:31.474
I got hands.

38:38.347 --> 38:40.190
What's up ?
My knuckleheads didn't post ?

38:40.470 --> 38:42.453
They did, but they left.

38:45.186 --> 38:45.878
Over here.

38:51.121 --> 38:52.787
You lookin' for
a discount, old man ?

38:53.463 --> 38:54.928
Naw, but I'm lookin' for you.

38:55.538 --> 38:56.912
Why somethin' come up missin' ?

38:57.415 --> 38:59.163
Came past to apologize.

38:59.632 --> 39:01.310
I'm new at this coachin' thin'.

39:01.321 --> 39:03.421
An' I got us off on the wrong foot.

39:04.008 --> 39:07.723
I ain't gonna leave it between us,
you thinkin' I gave up on y'all.

39:08.323 --> 39:11.537
Motherfucker's memory weak as shit.
We the ones bailed out on him.

39:14.329 --> 39:16.238
Anyway, I'm here now.

39:21.996 --> 39:22.919
Let me understand:

39:22.954 --> 39:25.581
You want to sell drug traffickers
a series of cell phones

39:25.582 --> 39:27.893
that are pre-approved
for telephonic intercepts.

39:28.644 --> 39:29.828
And you want me

39:30.368 --> 39:33.384
to sign off on court-ordered taps
on a bunch of phones that

39:33.403 --> 39:34.928
at the time I am signing the order

39:34.986 --> 39:38.282
have not been used for any
illegal activity whatsoever.

39:38.822 --> 39:40.754
If you're looking for
precedents, your honor ?

39:40.777 --> 39:41.540
There aren't any.

39:41.563 --> 39:44.320
It's circumstantial P.C. at best.

39:49.645 --> 39:50.866
What the hell, let's do it.

39:51.698 --> 39:55.287
Let the court of appeals sort it
out, if it even gets that far.

40:05.326 --> 40:06.322
Quite the legal mind.

40:33.111 --> 40:33.933
Buy you a drink ?

40:34.707 --> 40:36.349
Why the fuck
you comin' up behind me ?

40:36.901 --> 40:37.557
Sorry.

40:57.084 --> 40:57.763
Bushy Top.

40:58.257 --> 41:00.602
You called, I didn't know if
I'd find you here so late.

41:00.614 --> 41:02.432
Just getting ready
for COMSTAT tomorrow.

41:02.655 --> 41:03.675
So what's up, Major ?

41:08.221 --> 41:09.770
Your unit is still working...

41:10.626 --> 41:11.834
a drug war, right ?

41:11.869 --> 41:12.913
Working it hard.

41:13.969 --> 41:17.258
Does the name Avon Barksdale
do anythin' for you ?

41:18.224 --> 41:19.068
He's a player ?

41:19.184 --> 41:20.111
He's the main guy.

41:20.523 --> 41:22.892
We thought he was down,
but he popped up in september.

41:23.385 --> 41:25.386
You add him to the equation,
it goes a long way

41:25.411 --> 41:26.641
to explaining the violence.

41:28.109 --> 41:30.032
So it wouldn't be
a stretch if he got shot ?

41:30.219 --> 41:31.216
You heard he got shot ?

41:32.471 --> 41:34.580
You know when or where ?
I could run it out quick.

41:34.614 --> 41:36.057
Naw, ain't gonna make no difference

41:36.070 --> 41:38.556
he didn't post up at an
emergency room from what I hear.

41:41.582 --> 41:44.804
Major, I'm gonna be straight with you.
We're runnin' wires into his people

41:45.684 --> 41:47.209
but we're barely
above the street.

41:47.232 --> 41:49.227
So far, we haven't even
put an eyeball on him.

41:54.870 --> 41:56.430
Suppose to be layin' his head there.

41:57.638 --> 42:00.348
I need you to check that out,
get back to me as soon as you can.

42:00.372 --> 42:01.426
You got a C.I., huh ?

42:01.627 --> 42:03.748
You wanna see if your
man's creds are bonafide.

42:04.967 --> 42:06.435
Don't try to play me, Bushy Top.

42:07.103 --> 42:08.932
I didn't say male,
I didn't say female.

42:10.058 --> 42:10.516
Alright.

42:11.197 --> 42:12.991
I'll get a surveillance
goin' right away.

42:13.062 --> 42:15.755
According to my source,
Barksdale's name is on the paperwork.

42:15.860 --> 42:16.563
No shit.

42:18.840 --> 42:21.350
You get the confirmation on
that, call me back on my cell.

42:24.540 --> 42:26.147
Good luck tomorrow.

42:26.323 --> 42:26.957
Yeah, right.

42:57.213 --> 42:57.892
Sham.

43:00.662 --> 43:01.447
Shamrock.

43:03.499 --> 43:05.165
Run these over to Levy for me.

43:05.447 --> 43:06.773
Tell him I want a read on it.

43:07.370 --> 43:08.180
A read ?

43:08.990 --> 43:09.787
Fresh eyes.

43:10.878 --> 43:12.309
Tell him I'll call him tomorrow.

43:12.814 --> 43:13.306
A-ight.

43:20.550 --> 43:21.899
Come on, Mr. Bodyguard.

43:52.230 --> 43:54.095
And so, we're gonna
come at her like that.

43:54.553 --> 43:56.559
So you gonna give me
these phones to sell ?

43:57.157 --> 43:58.716
The money comes back, Bubs.

43:59.010 --> 43:59.585
All of it ?

44:04.857 --> 44:06.746
- Is that Beadie Russell ?
- Looks like.

44:09.713 --> 44:11.708
Whoa, yo, you can't
turn from this lane.

44:17.583 --> 44:18.932
Sweet Beatrice Russ...

44:23.324 --> 44:24.521
I was just gonna say, "hey."

44:30.679 --> 44:31.664
North and Pulaski.

44:32.568 --> 44:35.761
The photo was taken at four P.M.,
prime time for street-level dealing.

44:38.072 --> 44:39.749
That is Riggs and Calhoun.

44:41.145 --> 44:42.248
Mount and Fayette.

44:43.116 --> 44:44.088
Edmondson and Brice.

44:44.711 --> 44:46.073
It's your old foot post, Deputy.

44:47.058 --> 44:48.418
I know where it is, Major...

44:49.521 --> 44:52.442
what I don't know and
very much want to know is

44:52.852 --> 44:54.741
where is the west
Baltimore drug trade ?

44:55.421 --> 44:59.323
I hope, major, these are not staged
photographs you're showing us.

44:59.347 --> 45:00.802
No, sir, they are not.

45:01.985 --> 45:04.109
No, Deputy, I found another approach.

45:04.567 --> 45:05.704
I'm all ears, Bunny.

45:06.667 --> 45:07.864
I moved them off the corners.

45:07.924 --> 45:11.219
Goddamnit, don't be coy
with me, Major. I can see that.

45:11.946 --> 45:14.609
What I want to know is how the
fuck you managed to move them

45:14.844 --> 45:16.275
and where the fuck they are now.

45:18.128 --> 45:18.762
Deputy

45:21.072 --> 45:23.184
I don't know quite
how to put this, but we...

45:24.721 --> 45:25.565
I mean, I...

45:27.383 --> 45:29.842
I began by identifying those
areas of my district where

45:29.843 --> 45:31.822
drug trafficking was least harmful

45:32.071 --> 45:35.497
I proceeded to push all street-level
dealing towards those areas.

45:36.060 --> 45:37.092
Now at first

45:37.925 --> 45:41.147
dealing with the juveniles
on them corners, had little success.

45:42.050 --> 45:43.869
But ultimately

45:44.666 --> 45:48.081
by rounding up all the mid-level
dealers in my district

45:48.853 --> 45:50.776
and making an offer
they couldn't refuse

45:50.859 --> 45:52.794
- I was able to...
- You made them an offer ?

45:53.662 --> 45:54.260
Yes, sir.

45:57.674 --> 46:02.430
Either they move their people
to one of three designated areas

46:03.310 --> 46:05.949
where drug enforcement was
not a district priority...

46:07.052 --> 46:10.008
or they face the wrath of every
able-bodied soul in my district.

46:14.199 --> 46:15.429
Major, I don't understand.

46:15.970 --> 46:17.669
The only time we can
hold a drug corner

46:17.670 --> 46:19.559
is when we assign
officers to stand there.

46:20.298 --> 46:23.473
Your slides don't suggest any
concerted deployment on any corners.

46:24.246 --> 46:25.501
How were you able to...

46:25.525 --> 46:28.293
Jesus christ, you nit,
don't you see what he's done.

46:29.360 --> 46:30.652
He's legalized drugs !

46:31.891 --> 46:34.155
Actually, I elected to ignore them.

46:34.801 --> 46:37.440
You lost your fucking mind.
He's lost his fucking mind.

46:38.672 --> 46:42.038
You. In my office. Now !

46:44.988 --> 46:46.149
That's it, gentleman.

47:12.930 --> 47:13.634
She's a go.

47:14.279 --> 47:15.230
Showtime, Bubs.

47:28.585 --> 47:29.758
Oh, shit.

47:30.908 --> 47:31.975
Sister Squeak.

47:32.280 --> 47:33.172
Bottom-end Bubbles.

47:33.852 --> 47:34.813
How you stand, girl ?

47:35.013 --> 47:35.905
Been a long time.

47:36.501 --> 47:37.428
T-shirts ?

47:37.603 --> 47:39.527
<i>What the hell kinda
money is in t-shirts ?</i>

47:39.843 --> 47:41.098
<i>Girl, you just don't know.</i>

47:41.275 --> 47:42.242
<i>But how's your game ?</i>

47:42.278 --> 47:43.426
<i>I heard you was locked up.</i>

47:43.438 --> 47:45.206
<i>Shit, I been on paper for a year.</i>

47:45.440 --> 47:47.459
<i>- I got some things going.
- I can see that.</i>

47:47.834 --> 47:48.701
<i>You look good.</i>

47:48.726 --> 47:49.476
How's he doing ?

47:49.887 --> 47:51.341
He'd talk a cat off a fish cart.

47:51.658 --> 47:53.042
<i>A-ight, Bubs, I gotta get.</i>

47:53.501 --> 47:54.839
Alright, I see you later on.

47:58.323 --> 47:59.214
Yo, Squeak, Squeak.

47:59.894 --> 48:00.774
I 'bout forgot.

48:01.513 --> 48:03.356
I can sell you one
of these, real cheap.

48:03.366 --> 48:04.711
If you got use for the shits...

48:08.418 --> 48:10.025
I'm fuckin' dead.

48:10.682 --> 48:12.207
You mean, we're fuckin' dead.

48:12.360 --> 48:13.802
We're all dead behind this shit.

48:14.753 --> 48:16.008
Jesus christ.

48:16.946 --> 48:19.034
What I did, I did knowingly
and on my own.

48:20.266 --> 48:22.095
My men had nothin' to do with this.

48:22.458 --> 48:24.605
They thought it was part
of some elaborate trap.

48:25.775 --> 48:28.672
So if you need me to fall on
that sword, I'm good with that.

48:29.587 --> 48:30.644
You're good with it ?

48:31.042 --> 48:34.984
Hey, you know I got my vacation time,
my last 30 in a couple months.

48:35.828 --> 48:37.529
So, if you need me
to fall, I'm ready.

48:39.101 --> 48:40.930
But don't let me hear
that you're taking

48:40.931 --> 48:42.668
any punitive action
against my people.

48:43.406 --> 48:44.801
Because I can get on the soapbox

48:44.802 --> 48:47.499
and I can lie as good as
the next man, if I have to.

48:48.812 --> 48:50.466
Are you threatening me ?

48:52.965 --> 48:54.126
I believe I am, sir.

48:55.767 --> 48:56.623
My apologies.

48:58.406 --> 49:01.502
Bunny, you cocksucker, I got
give it to you, a brilliant idea.

49:01.843 --> 49:05.538
Insane and illegal, but stone
fuckin' brilliant nonetheless.

49:07.424 --> 49:08.725
After all my puttin' my foot up

49:08.726 --> 49:11.013
people's asses to decrease
the numbers, he comes in

49:11.471 --> 49:15.612
and in one stroke, gets
a fuckin' 14% decrease.

49:16.538 --> 49:19.683
Fuckin' shame it's gonna
end our careers, but still.

49:21.818 --> 49:24.164
You're all probably tired
of hearin' from me, but...

49:29.290 --> 49:30.228
I brought these.

49:31.354 --> 49:32.175
Letters...

49:32.961 --> 49:36.598
from community associations,
ministers, business people, citizens.

49:38.392 --> 49:39.514
And they're all positive.

49:40.968 --> 49:43.419
They're all happy that the
dealers are off the corners.

49:44.486 --> 49:47.127
You think that's
gonna save our asses ?

49:48.534 --> 49:49.108
Do you ?

49:50.359 --> 49:51.885
No, I guess not, but...

49:53.491 --> 49:55.052
that and my badge is all I got.

49:55.297 --> 49:59.356
I might have your badge,
Major, but not today.

50:00.048 --> 50:03.707
I don't want to draw any attention
to this shit before we're...

50:04.176 --> 50:05.491
ready to speak to it.

50:06.746 --> 50:10.686
So if you have any vacation
time, you're taking it now.

50:11.506 --> 50:16.021
Do not report for
a shift until notified.

50:27.272 --> 50:28.011
Oh...

50:30.028 --> 50:31.190
one more thing, sir.

50:32.373 --> 50:34.832
A "Sun" reporter is
aware of my deployment.

50:36.144 --> 50:37.939
I told him an investigation
was pending

50:38.925 --> 50:40.344
he promised to delay the article.

50:41.400 --> 50:41.904
How long ?

50:42.901 --> 50:45.306
About a week, tops.

50:51.425 --> 50:54.267
I was with Superstroke on the
pool circuit in the early days.

50:54.466 --> 50:56.625
But mostly pickpocketin'
and short cons.

50:57.364 --> 51:00.871
I did the long distance access card
heist before cell phones got popular.

51:01.399 --> 51:02.267
You crept numbers ?

51:03.358 --> 51:05.438
Yeah, I favored the airports, yeah.

51:05.790 --> 51:07.004
Can you still read numbers ?

51:07.420 --> 51:08.312
What's up with this ?

51:08.334 --> 51:10.411
Your man thinkin' I brought
him bad merchandise ?

51:10.423 --> 51:12.839
'Cause if that what he think,
we can beat feet right now.

51:12.848 --> 51:15.394
Damn, Bernard, why you
actin' all C.I.A. and shit ?

51:15.440 --> 51:16.883
We tryin' to make money here.

51:16.953 --> 51:18.642
If you had to answer
to the people I do

51:18.666 --> 51:20.670
your ass would be damn
more sight cautious, too.

51:20.683 --> 51:21.586
That's all I'm sayin'.

51:21.610 --> 51:22.501
I appreciate caution.

51:23.130 --> 51:24.642
'Cause I'm hangin' out here too.

51:26.038 --> 51:26.753
Give it a go.

51:27.481 --> 51:28.255
Use a cell phone.

51:39.244 --> 51:41.378
Marlene, you send
that copy off to Paris ?

51:42.505 --> 51:43.396
Thank you, darling.

51:44.522 --> 51:46.040
That will work, I'm at the airport.

51:46.531 --> 51:47.506
The shuttle, yes...

52:06.486 --> 52:15.084
three, one, oh, double four, eight,
sixteen, ninety-one, double seven

52:15.448 --> 52:20.477
eight, three, one, two.
Now that last number might be a seven.

52:20.512 --> 52:23.093
I'm not too sure with
these small keypads and all.

52:23.691 --> 52:24.735
We can do business.

52:28.752 --> 52:29.315
That's it.

52:30.054 --> 52:32.388
One two, one two, one two.

52:33.549 --> 52:34.557
One two, that's it.

52:35.297 --> 52:36.541
One two, there you go.

52:37.591 --> 52:39.879
Alright, there it is.
Now you gettin' it.

52:40.477 --> 52:41.603
Keep that left hand up.

52:45.252 --> 52:45.838
Hey.

52:46.530 --> 52:46.977
Hey.

52:48.685 --> 52:49.331
Alright.

52:49.554 --> 52:50.797
Watch your balance now.

52:50.961 --> 52:51.829
Don't lean forward.

52:51.830 --> 52:54.050
Don't lean too much, don't
lean too forward, alright ?

52:54.071 --> 52:56.463
Alright, let's go. Don't lean
too forward, that's right.

52:56.744 --> 52:57.859
One two, pivot...

52:58.128 --> 52:58.934
You're kidding.

52:59.955 --> 53:01.773
Tell me he's kidding.

53:03.520 --> 53:04.599
You're kidding, right ?

53:05.773 --> 53:08.494
He did it without our knowledge.

53:08.635 --> 53:09.858
Without your knowledge.

53:10.515 --> 53:12.685
Well, that's worse.
You're the Commissioner...

53:13.201 --> 53:14.526
Was the Commissioner.

53:15.593 --> 53:18.538
You think the buck's gonna stop
in this office, you're wrong.

53:18.913 --> 53:23.919
If I might, these are letters
from people in his district.

53:24.764 --> 53:27.462
Ministers, business
people, voters...

53:28.270 --> 53:29.490
all glowing reports.

53:30.241 --> 53:34.440
And there's the 14% reduction
in crime, in the Western.

53:35.402 --> 53:37.220
That's not an anomaly.

53:38.030 --> 53:39.261
It's hard data.

53:40.505 --> 53:42.926
Now, we can clean it up,
make it go away.

53:43.853 --> 53:45.589
The press might already
have wind of it

53:45.600 --> 53:49.495
but we can explain that as
some sort of a new initiative.

53:50.351 --> 53:52.111
Trap high-end drug dealers...

53:53.651 --> 53:54.461
14% ?

53:55.669 --> 53:59.809
If we handle this right, we
might all get out from underneath.

54:00.419 --> 54:01.662
No mud on anybody.

54:04.644 --> 54:06.134
No, no.

54:07.883 --> 54:10.264
I trusted you, Erv, I really did.

54:10.756 --> 54:11.882
You let me down.

54:12.715 --> 54:14.841
Now, this thing goes wrong,
no tellin' the damage.

54:14.864 --> 54:16.353
On this, you walk point.

54:16.553 --> 54:19.157
That's the way things work, Erv.
You know it as well as I do.

54:26.263 --> 54:27.037
Thank you, Ervin.

54:28.808 --> 54:30.849
I'll be over shortly
to see the detailed plan

54:30.871 --> 54:33.019
on how this shit gets
cleaned up immediately.

54:50.612 --> 54:53.579
If you could call this shit
something other than what it is...

54:53.732 --> 54:54.916
Don't even think it.

55:01.244 --> 55:02.464
Way it works is this:

55:02.781 --> 55:06.124
If you don't re-up the minutes
on your cell phone before 60 days

55:06.312 --> 55:08.361
the wireless company
recycles the phone number.

55:08.408 --> 55:09.734
And that's where I get them.

55:10.215 --> 55:13.053
I put the word out on the street
that I'm buying tossed-off burners.

55:13.065 --> 55:14.308
Payin' two dollars a pop.

55:14.566 --> 55:16.290
Street people bring me hundreds.

55:16.666 --> 55:19.150
I bring 'em in here to my niece
she jiggles the computer

55:19.162 --> 55:22.164
juices them up another 200
minutes on a bogus account.

55:22.740 --> 55:27.008
And that automatically extends the
life of the phone for another 60 days.

55:27.571 --> 55:29.957
She charges me 20
on each phone on her end.

55:30.298 --> 55:32.607
I double it or more
on the street to make mine.

55:33.335 --> 55:34.403
So what you sayin' ?

55:35.481 --> 55:37.554
Baby, a standard
Trac phone, with two

55:37.566 --> 55:40.405
maybe 400 minutes on it
gonna run you 150, 200, easy.

55:41.260 --> 55:45.131
I charge you an even 100,
you clear 50 on each phone.

55:45.237 --> 55:47.315
That's if'in you can back
them up with receipts.

55:47.421 --> 55:49.955
I gotta show receipts lookin'
like they from different places

55:49.978 --> 55:50.705
or I can't play.

55:52.594 --> 55:54.119
Can we accommodate the good man ?

55:54.705 --> 55:56.769
Damn, Calvin, you know
I got the bingo tonight.

56:09.631 --> 56:11.978
Look, friend, I ain't sure
you want to be around here.

56:12.153 --> 56:14.382
And I'm damn sure we're
gettin' tired of havin' you.

56:14.406 --> 56:15.298
That plain enough ?

56:15.320 --> 56:16.305
You should know by now

56:16.329 --> 56:18.710
I don't wanna be 'round no
bunch of cocksucking faggots.

56:19.028 --> 56:21.455
But I ain't gonna stop coming
round till I run up on Omar.

56:21.561 --> 56:23.122
You might want to get the word out.

56:23.191 --> 56:25.338
For the last time,
I don't know him.

56:25.572 --> 56:27.040
Then I'm back tomorrow.

56:51.997 --> 56:52.993
Maybe I can help you ?

56:58.600 --> 56:59.949
I don't doubt it for a minute.

